title: Cafe in Love
overview: Kawee's coffee shop is about to close down. Because he can't make coffee at all, he had to find a way for the shop to survive. His older brother, Kawin, advised him to seek help from Phupha who opened a small coffee shop. Â He sees Phupha and a guy Paew, Kawee's best friend, so he proposes a plan: ask Kawee to lure Phupha to fall in love with him and ask him to help with the coffee shop. Kawee decided to follow the plan. But it's not as easy as you think...
